text: INTERVIEW: NASA scientist explains supermoon eclipse WSBTSep. 25, 2015. 06:13 AM EST In just three nights expect a very different sight. You could see something that hasn't been seen... More » In just three nights expect a very different sight. You could see something that hasn't been seen for more than 30 years. We're talking about the supermoon! This morning NASA scientist Dr. Alex Young joined WSBT 22 to explain. « Less Tags
